<h2 class="govuk-heading-l">When to use</h2>

<p class="govuk-body">
Use this pattern to tell users about changes to the UK Trade Tariff, Customs Handling of Import and Export Freight (CHIEF), Customs Declaration Service (CDS) and monthly trade euro rate.
</p>

<h2 class="govuk-heading-l">When not to use</h2>

<p class="govuk-body">
  Do not update a customs information paper after it's been published, unless it's to correct a typo. A new one must be issued.
</p>

